snippet.title: Castlevania Fighter - Nightmare Richter Belmont + EXTRA & PHANTASM (1CC, No Damage, No items)
snippet.description:
Tips:
-Richter is the character with the best mobility of the game, not using it is to condemn himself with the character.
-The recoil of each character is invincible The only thing that can not dodge are loads of bosses.
-The recoil can be extended if you move jumping almost instantly, this helps you avoid fast projectiles.
-The twists of your whip help you against the minios of the bosses, take advantage of it you can also cancel it with a recoil.
-It is good to use the balls to eliminate enemy minions.
